# PixieWorks by Elle Privacy Policy

This repository hosts the Privacy Policy page for PixieWorks by Elle.  
The policy is served via GitHub Pages at:  
https://<your-username>.github.io/privacy-policy.html

---

## Files

- `privacy-policy.html`  
  The full Privacy Policy in standalone HTML form.

- `README.md`  
  This file, explaining repo purpose and update instructions.

---

## How to Update

1. Clone the repo or edit directly in GitHub’s web editor.  
2. Modify the `privacy-policy.html` content as needed.  
3. Commit and push your changes to the `main` branch.  
4. Wait a minute—GitHub Pages will automatically publish your updates.

